A vintage 1960s style illustration of a conference hall filled with enthusiastic audience members, their faces glowing with excitement and satisfaction, holding up evaluation cards with stars. The scene is rendered in warm retro colors—burnt orange, mustard yellow, and teal—with a halftone dot pattern texture. In the foreground, two silhouetted presenters stand at a curved mid-century modern podium, bathed in spotlight beams. Floating above the crowd are abstract geometric shapes representing positive energy and applause, swirling upward like confetti. The composition has the optimistic, aspirational feel of vintage travel or educational posters from the atomic age.
